ors F.C.|Solihull Moors]]}}\n{{fs player|no=43|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=David Bremang|other=on loan at [[Leamington F.C.|Leamington]]}}\n{{fs player|no=50|nat=WAL|pos=GK|name=Cian Tyler|other=on loan at [[Barwell F.C.|Barwell]]}}\n{{fs end}}\n\n===Under-23 squad===\n{{updated|16 January 2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ccfc.co.uk/teams/Under-23s/|title=Under-23s - Coventry City|website=www.ccfc.co.uk}}</ref>\n{{fs start}}\n{{fs player|no=29|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Jak Hickman]]}}\n{{fs player|no=30|nat=NED|pos=MF|name=Bouwe Bosma}}\n{{fs player|no=39|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Daniel Bartlett (footballer)|Daniel Bartlett]]}}\n{{fs player|no=40|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=[[Jonny Ngandu]]}}\n{{fs player|no=41|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=[[Will Bapaga]]}}\n{{fs player|no=42|nat=ENG|pos=GK|name=Tom Bilson}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{fs player|no=44|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Charlie Wakefield (footballer, born 1998)|Charlie Wakefield]]}}\n{{fs player|no=45|nat=SCO|pos=MF|name=[[Jack Burroughs]]}}\n{{fs player|no=46|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Blaine Rowe}}\n{{fs player|no=47|nat=SCO|pos=MF|name=[[Jordan Young (footballer)|Jordan Young]]}}\n{{fs player|no=48|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Joe Newton}}\n{{fs end}}\n\n===Under-18 squad===\n{{updated|6 August 2019<ref>{{cite news|title=Introducing The Sky Blues Academy Scholars|url=https://www.ccfc.co.uk/news/2019/august/news-introducing-the-sky-blues-academy-scholars/|publisher=Coventry City Official Site|access-date=6 August 2019}}</ref>}}\n{{fs start}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=GK|name=Keelan Fallows}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=SCO|pos=DF|name=George Burroughs}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Kai Forsyth}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Callum Martin}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Adam Taylor}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Alexander Costa}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Matthew Harland}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=NIR|pos=MF|name=Daniel Lafferty}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Joseph Nightingale}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Sam Pitts-Eckersall}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=Hayden Purvis}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=Thai Duggan}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=Harrison Nee}}\n{{fs end}}\n\n==Backroom staff and club officials==\n{|\n|valign=\"top\"|\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Name\n!Position\n|-\n| [[Mark Robins]]\n| Manager\n|-\n| [[Adrian Viveash]]\n| Assistant Manager\n|-\n| Aled Williams\n| Goalkeeping Coach\n|-\n| Jason Farndon\n| First Team Coach\n|-\n| Luke Tisdale\n| Under 23s Coach\n|-\n| [[John Dempster (footballer)|John Dempster]]\n| Under 18s Coach\n|-\n| ''Daniel Bolas''\n| Academy Manager\n|-\n| Karl Hooper\n| Personal Development<br>Plan (PDP) Coach\n|-\n| Paul Godfrey\n| Physiotherapist\n|-\n| Paul Travis\n| Performance Analyst\n|-\n| Andy Young\n| Senior Fitness Coach\n|-\n| Chris Badlan<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.coventrytelegraph.net/sport/football/football-news/he-real-asset-coventry-city-14617649 |title={title} |access-date=5 May 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180505205359/https://www.coventrytelegraph.net/sport/football/football-news/he-real-asset-coventry-city-14617649 |archive-date=5 May 2018 |url-status=live |df=dmy-all |date=4 May 2018 }}</ref>\n| Head of Recruitment\n|-\n| [[Ray Gooding]]\n| Scout (Midlands Region)\n|}\n|valign=\"top\"|\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Name\n!Position\n|-\n| Joy Seppala\n| Owner (SISU)\n|-\n| Tim Fisher\n| Chairman\n|-\n| David Boddy\n| Chief Executive\n|-\n| [[George Curtis (footballer, born 1939)|George Curtis]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"| Life Presidents\n|-\n| [[John Sillett]]\n|-\n| [[David Busst]]\n| Head of ''Sky Blues<br>in the Community''\n|-\n| Jim Brown\n| Club Historian\n|}\n|}\n\n==Seasons, awards and honours==\n{{See also|List of Coventry City F.C. seasons|List of Coventry City F.C. records and statistics|Coventry City F.C. in European football}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 90%\"\n! Season Re