24424/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23548760|archive-date=21 January 2015|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref><br>\n{{sup|\u2020\u2020\u2020}} [[Bury F.C.|Bury]] were expelled from the EFL on 27 August 2019 due to financial issues at the club.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49451896 |title=Bury expelled by English Football League after takeover collapses |publisher=BBC Sport |date=28 August 2019 |accessdate=28 August 2019}}</ref><br>\n<nowiki>*</nowiki> Season in progress.\n\n===Club honours===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*'''[[FA Cup]]'''\n**Winners: [[1987 FA Cup Final|1986\u201387]]\n*'''[[Football League Cup]]'''\n**Semi-finalists: 1980\u201381, 1989\u201390\n*'''[[FA Community Shield|Charity Shield]]'''\n**Runners-up: [[1987 FA Charity Shield|1987]]\n*'''[[Football League Trophy]]'''\n**Winners: [[2017 EFL Trophy Final|2016\u201317]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Coventry City 2\u20131 Oxford United|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39404886|website=EFL Trophy Final|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=2 April 2017|date=2 April 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170402163558/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/39404886|archive-date=2 April 2017|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n**Northern Area Finalists: 2012\u201313\n*'''[[FA Youth Cup]]'''\n**Winners: [[FA Youth Cup Finals of the 1980s#1986\u201387: Coventry City vs Charlton Athletic (1\u20131 and 1\u20130 aet, 2\u20131 Aggregate)|1986\u201387]]\n**Runners-up: 1967\u201368, 1969\u201370, 1998\u201399, 1999\u201300\n*'''[[Full Members Cup]]'''\n**Semi-finalists: 1987\u201388\n*'''[[Football League Second Division]]''' (now '''[[Football League Championship]]''')\n**Champions: 1966\u201367\n*'''[[Football League Third Division]]''' (now '''[[Football League One]]''')\n**Champions: 1963\u201364\n*'''[[Football League Third Division South]]'''\n**Champions: 1935\u201336\n**Runners-up: 1933\u201334\n*'''[[Football League Fourth Division]]''' (now '''[[Football League Two]]