elli]]|other=on loan at [[Wrexham A.F.C.|Wrexham]]}}\n{{fs player|no=27|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Jordon Thompson]]|other=on loan at [[Wrexham A.F.C.|Wrexham]]}}\n{{fs player|no=28|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Callum Maycock]]|other=on loan at [[Leamington F.C.|Leamington]]}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{fs player|no=32|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Dexter Walters]]|other=on loan at [[Leamington F.C.|Leamington]]}}\n{{fs player|no=35|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Declan Drysdale]]|other=on loan at [[Solihull Moors F.C.|Solihull Moors]]}}\n{{fs player|no=43|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=David Bremang|other=on loan at [[Leamington F.C.|Leamington]]}}\n{{fs player|no=50|nat=WAL|pos=GK|name=Cian Tyler|other=on loan at [[Barwell F.C.|Barwell]]}}\n{{fs end}}\n\n===Under-23 squad===\n{{updated|16 January 2020}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ccfc.co.uk/teams/Under-23s/|title=Under-23s - Coventry City|website=www.ccfc.co.uk}}</ref>\n{{fs start}}\n{{fs player|no=29|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=[[Jak Hickman]]}}\n{{fs player|no=30|nat=NED|pos=MF|name=Bouwe Bosma}}\n{{fs player|no=39|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Daniel Bartlett (footballer)|Daniel Bartlett]]}}\n{{fs player|no=40|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=[[Jonny Ngandu]]}}\n{{fs player|no=41|nat=ENG|pos=FW|name=[[Will Bapaga]]}}\n{{fs player|no=42|nat=ENG|pos=GK|name=Tom Bilson}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{fs player|no=44|nat=ENG|pos=MF|name=[[Charlie Wakefield (footballer, born 1998)|Charlie Wakefield]]}}\n{{fs player|no=45|nat=SCO|pos=MF|name=[[Jack Burroughs]]}}\n{{fs player|no=46|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Blaine Rowe}}\n{{fs player|no=47|nat=SCO|pos=MF|name=[[Jordan Young (footballer)|Jordan Young]]}}\n{{fs player|no=48|nat=ENG|pos=DF|name=Joe Newton}}\n{{fs end}}\n\n===Under-18 squad===\n{{updated|6 August 2019<ref>{{cite news|title=Introducing The Sky Blues Academy Scholars|url=https://www.ccfc.co.uk/news/2019/august/news-introducing-the-sky-blues-academy-scholars/|publisher=Coventry City Official Site|access-date=6 August 2019}}</ref>}}\n{{fs start}}\n{{fs player|no=\u2014|nat=ENG|pos=GK|name=Keelan Fallows}}