[[1997\u201398 FA Premier League|1997\u20131998]])<br>{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Ian Wallace (footballer)|Ian Wallace]], 23 ([[1977\u201378 in English football|1977\u20131978]])\n|-\n|Oldest player to play in a first-team match || {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Alf Wood (footballer, born 1915)|Alf Wood]], 43 years 207 days (vs [[Plymouth Argyle F.C.|Plymouth Argyle]], 1958)\n|-\n|Youngest player to play in a first-team match || {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jonson Clarke-Harris]], 16 years 21 days (substitute vs [[Morecambe F.C.|Morecambe]], 2010)\n|-\n|Youngest player to start a first-team match || {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Brian Hill (footballer, born 1941)|Brian Hill]], 16 years 273 days (vs [[Gillingham F.C.|Gillingham]], 1958)\n|}\n\n==Managers==\n{{See also|List of Coventry City F.C. managers}}\n{{columns-list|\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[William Stanley (football manager)|William Stanley]] (1883\u20131885)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Harry Hathaway]] (1885\u20131887)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[J.G. Morgan]] (1887\u20131892)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Teddy Kirk]] (1893)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[George Maley]] (1893)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Joe Collins (football manager)|Joe Collins]] (1893\u20131895)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Tom Cashmore]] (1895\u20131900)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ben Newhall]] (1900\u20131902)\n*{{flagicon|IRL}} [[Michael O'Shea (football manager)|Michael O'Shea]] (1902\u20131905)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Joe Beaman]] (1905\u20131908)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Walter Harris (football manager)|Walter Harris]] (1908\u20131909)\n*{{flagicon|IRL}} [[Harry Buckle]] (1909\u20131911)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Robert Wallace (football manager)|Robert Wallace]] & committee (1911\u20131914)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Frank Scott-Walford]] & committee (1914\u20131915)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[H. Howard]] & committee (1915\u20131916)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[William Clayton (football manager)|William Clayton]] (1917\u20131919)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Harry Pollitt (football manager)|Harry Pollitt]] (1919\u20131920)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Albert Evans (footballer,