1995)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ron Atkinson]] (1995\u20131996)\n*{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Gordon Strachan]] (1996\u20132001)\n*{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Roland Nilsson]] (2001\u20132002)\n*<small>{{flagicon|ENG|size=15px}} [[Steve Ogrizovic]] & {{flagicon|ENG|size=15px}} [[Trevor Peake]] (caretakers) (2002)</small>\n*{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Gary McAllister]] (2002\u20132003)\n*{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Eric Black]] (2003\u20132004)\n*<small>{{flagicon|ENG|size=15px}} [[Steve Ogrizovic]] (caretaker) (2004)</small>\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Peter Reid]] (2004\u20132005)\n*<small>{{flagicon|ENG|size=15px}} [[Adrian Heath]] (caretaker) (2005)</small>\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Micky Adams]] (2005\u20132007)\n*<small>{{flagicon|ENG|size=15px}} [[Adrian Heath]] (caretaker) (2007)</small>\n*{{flagicon|NIR}} [[Iain Dowie]] (2007\u20132008)\n*<small>{{flagicon|ENG|size=15px}} [[Frankie Bunn]] & {{flagicon|AUS|size=15px}} [[John Harbin]] (caretakers) (2008)</small>\n*{{flagicon|WAL}} [[Chris Coleman (footballer)|Chris Coleman]] (2008\u20132010)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Aidy Boothroyd]] (2010\u20132011)\n*<small>{{flagicon|ENG|size=15px}} [[Steve Harrison (footballer)|Steve Harrison]] & {{flagicon|ENG|size=15px}} [[Andy Thorn (footballer)|Andy Thorn]] (caretakers) (2011)</small>\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Andy Thorn (footballer)|Andy Thorn]] (2011\u20132012)\n*<small>{{flagicon|ENG|size=15px}} [[Richard Shaw (footballer)|Richard Shaw]] & {{flagicon|IRL|size=15px}} [[Lee Carsley]] (caretakers) (2012)</small>\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mark Robins]] (2012\u20132013)\n*<small>{{flagicon|IRL|size=15px}} [[Lee Carsley]] (caretaker) (2013)</small>\n*{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Steven Pressley]] (2013\u20132015)\n*<small>{{flagicon|SCO|size=15px}} [[Neil MacFarlane (footballer)|Neil MacFarlane]] & {{flagicon|ENG|size=15px}} [[Dave Hockaday]] (caretakers) (2015)</small>\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Tony Mowbray]] (2015\u20132016)\n*<small>{{flagicon|ENG|size=15px}} [[Mark Venus]] (caretaker) (2016)</small>\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Russell Slade]] (2016\u20132017)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mark Robins]] (2017\u2013)\n}}\n\n==Chairmen==\n{{See also|Category:Coventry City F.C. directors and chairmen}}\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Thomas Owen (businessman)|Thomas Owen]] (1907\u20131912)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[David Cooke (businessman)|David Cooke]] (1912\u20131928)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Walter Brandish]] (1928\u20131935)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Fred Stringer]] (1935\u20131946)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[George Jones (businessman)|George Jones]] (1946\u20131954)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Eric Shanks]] (1954\u20131958)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Walter Brandish Jr.]] (1958\u20131960)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Derrick Robins]] (1960\u20131973)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Peter Robins]] (1973\u20131975)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jack Scamp]] (1975\u20131977)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Phil Mead (businessman)|Phil Mead]] (1977\u20131980)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jimmy Hill]] (1980\u20131983)\n*{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Iain Jamieson]] (1983\u20131984)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[John Poynton (businessman)|John Poynton]] (1984\u20131990)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Peter Robins]] (1990\u20131993)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[John Clarke (British businessman)|John Clarke]] (1993)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Bryan Richardson]] (1993\u20132002)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Mike McGinnity]] (2002\u20132005)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Geoffrey Robinson]] (2005\u20132007)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Joe Elliott (businessman)|Joe Elliott]] (2007)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ray Ranson]] (2007\u20132011)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ken Dulieu]] (2011)\n*Vacant (2011\u20132014)\n*{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Tim Fisher (businessman)|Tim Fisher]] (2014\u2013)\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Coventry City F.C.}}\n*[http://www.ccfc.co.uk/ Official club website]\n*{{BBC Football Info|BBClinkname=coventry-city}}\n* Soccerbase \u2013 [http://www.soccerbase.com/results2.sd?teamid=621 Results] | [http://www.soccerbase.com/squad_season.sd?teamid=621 Squad Stats] | [https://web.archive.org/web/20090731111517/http://